and thought of you as an apprentice.

01:02:49.849 --> 01:02:51.641
He wanted you to continue his work.

01:02:51.684 --> 01:02:54.060
But I'm not a letter writer.

01:02:54.103 --> 01:02:55.937
I can't write like he did.

01:02:55.980 --> 01:03:00.525
Don't worry, you'll know what to do.

01:03:00.568 --> 01:03:05.071
Let's sing our song.
It'll cheer us up.

01:03:05.114 --> 01:03:07.991
Sam would have liked that.

01:03:08.034 --> 01:03:12.537
I'm sorry, I just... I really don't
feel like singing today.

01:04:27.530 --> 01:04:32.826
I am the resurrection, amen.

01:05:40.853 --> 01:05:44.940
 Bring down the house,
you lost me in shadow 

01:05:44.982 --> 01:05:48.902
 We're breathing it now,
run from the day glow. 

01:05:50.780 --> 01:05:53.531
That's my song.

01:05:53.574 --> 01:05:55.909
They're playing my song.

01:05:55.952 --> 01:05:58.203
 Feeling so bad,
it's burning, we're fleeing 

01:05:58.245 --> 01:06:02.540
 Deep, deep in ash,
falls like a powder 

01:06:02.583 --> 01:06:07.629
 Photos and cash,
it doesn't matter

01:06:07.672 --> 01:06:10.215
Kimmy.

01:06:10.257 --> 01:06:13.885
You know... life is like a mirror.

01:06:13.928 --> 01:06:17.514
And what you see is eventually
what you're going to get.

01:06:17.556 --> 01:06:21.434
And at some point it all reflects
back on you.

01:06:21.477 --> 01:06:28.775
I saw you at the concert.
It hurt.

01:06:28.818 --> 01:06:35.115
But I have to admit, you were great.

01:06:35.157 --> 01:06:38.493
I think the band is really lucky
to have you.

01:06:41.956 --> 01:06:46.376
I really hope you find
what you're looking for.

01:06:52.758 --> 01:06:57.220
I think I understand now what Sam
was trying to teach me.

01:06:57.263 --> 01:06:59.806
And what was that?

01:06:59.849 --> 01:07:03.685
He didn't want me to be a letter writer.

01:07:03.728 --> 01:07:07.522
He wanted me to use my own talent
to bless other people's lives

01:07:07.565 --> 01:07:09.733
just like he did with his.

01:07:09.775 --> 01:07:13.278
- And I know what that is now.
- You do?

01:07:13.320 --> 01:07:17.198
It's my voice.
That's my talent.

01:07:17.241 --> 01:07:21.786
I love to sing, I just never used it
for good or to help others.

01:07:21.829 --> 01:07:27.584
You knew it all along, didn't you?
And Sam probably did, too.

01:07:27.626 --> 01:07:29.586
That's why you asked me
to join the choir.

01:07:33.007 --> 01:07:36.968
